1011
01:16:27,796 --> 01:16:29,127
Well, it just so happens

1012
01:16:29,798 --> 01:16:33,427
that yesterday morning, I sold my car.

1013
01:16:33,635 --> 01:16:37,071
A dandy little 1932 Plymouth.

1014
01:16:37,372 --> 01:16:39,567
It's all here, 150 bucks.

1015
01:16:40,275 --> 01:16:43,108
- I don't have that kind of money.
