1019
01:16:50,852 --> 01:16:52,217
That's a lot of money.

1020
01:16:52,420 --> 01:16:53,717
What's the matter, William?

1021
01:16:53,922 --> 01:16:55,890
Are you losing your nerve?

1022
01:16:57,425 --> 01:16:59,222
- I got 40.
- I got 60.

1023
01:17:01,963 --> 01:17:04,056
Hundred and fifty bucks, straight pool.

1024
01:17:04,266 --> 01:17:05,494
First one to a hundred.

1025
01:17:05,700 --> 01:17:09,864
Is that okay with you, Bud,
or was it Lou?

1026
01:17:10,071 --> 01:17:12,403
- Call it.
- Heads.

1027
01:17:13,174 --> 01:17:15,472
Tails. You break.

1028
01:17:20,215 --> 01:17:22,115
Fourteen in the corner.

1029
01:17:25,053 --> 01:17:27,146
Two, corner.

1030
01:17:32,928 --> 01:17:35,419
Five, cross corner.

1031
01:17:40,569 --> 01:17:42,537
- So?
- Seven in the side.

1032
01:17:42,737 --> 01:17:44,295
- He's good.
- How good?

1033
01:17:44,506 --> 01:17:46,599
- Thirteen in the corner.
- A lot better than he was

1034
01:17:46,808 --> 01:17:47,832
five minutes ago.

1035
